{"tid":2196643,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遊樂中心為明日重開準備　設施之間加隔板加強清潔按鈕","createTime":"2020-09-10T05:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T05:17:58.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4647396b73841f378d170deca2aa42b273805d","tid":2196643,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:12:48.000Z","msg":"政府明日凌晨起放寬部分社交距離措施，部分處所可以重新，包括家庭遊樂中心、遊戲中心、麻將天九耍樂處所等。<br />\n<br />\n其中在荃灣，一間設有氣墊球機、擲彩虹等多種玩樂設施的家庭遊樂中心，正為重開作準備。有員工說，已在機器之間加設隔板，會特別清潔機器的按鈕等手部會接觸的位置，明日重開後亦會增加清潔次數。客人入店前要先量體溫及戴口罩，如有需要亦可拿取即棄手套使用。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548850-20200910.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548850-20200910.htm&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=8d2e0906\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548850-20200910.htm&h=95da3753\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548850-20200910.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1548850_1_20200910123150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1548850_1_20200910123150.jpg&h=def18e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7afd1ed340b4fb7a466745813c6f2a18107dfc2","tid":2196643,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾有趣"},{"pid":"29fbfb41b7b95d6f988c0beb70b54d9ff9f26b9a","tid":2196643,"uid":53601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim